                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14135754" author="benedict" created="Tue, 16 Sep 2014 17:19:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Could you give this patch a try?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It simply avoids passing through the extra RF option if it isn&apos;t the SimpleStrategy and it isn&apos;t specified explicitly by the user, so should fix it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14135794" author="yukim" created="Tue, 16 Sep 2014 17:41:11 +0000"  >&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;strategy.equals(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;org.apache.cassandra.locator.SimpleStrategy&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;strategy&lt;/tt&gt; here is &lt;tt&gt;OptionSimple&lt;/tt&gt; object so equality is always false. so when no &lt;tt&gt;-schema&lt;/tt&gt; it fails to create replication strategy.&lt;br/&gt;
Otherwise, it works for NTS.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14135799" author="benedict" created="Tue, 16 Sep 2014 17:43:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks. Fixed (v2). Will commit after you +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14135907" author="yukim" created="Tue, 16 Sep 2014 18:30:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14136079" author="benedict" created="Tue, 16 Sep 2014 19:50:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;thanks&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15203619" author="dins2k2" created="Mon, 21 Mar 2016 01:32:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi, So what is the command to be used for assigning the replication_factor for multiple DCs (like DC1=2,DC2=1,DC=3) in stress along with NTS through CCM? Thanks, Dinesh&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
